{"tid":201784,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"如果你男朋友/女朋友係重要日子去旅行⋯⋯","createTime":"2017-04-15T04:39:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-15T05:30:04.000Z","uid":4998,"like":15,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fe877b56fded12d1bbb1c131919a02f25799af6d","tid":201784,"uid":4998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T04:39:05.000Z","msg":"姐係可能一週年/你生日既時候話<br />\n要同班朋友去旅行 對象：成班中同/大同<br />\n大家覺得嬲是否合理？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 合理，因為你佢根本唔重視你，係我都嬲啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 講到尾咪又係一日，去個旅行都唔撚比"},{"pid":"5a589d67d4cdabced2f6a5f5caf967d12fc389a4","tid":201784,"uid":91069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T05:03:19.000Z","msg":"生日就誇d <br />\n一周年就是但啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我係咁諗"},{"pid":"3005e9fa14a096af8c1c5ffbdcbb7c2769cfe744","tid":201784,"uid":4998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T05:07:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>生日就誇d <br />\n一周年就是但啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我係咁諗</blockquote><br />\n如果前者呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db8263f582981abd5b33f14536058055fb9b53ab","tid":201784,"uid":46609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T05:08:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>生日就誇d <br />\n一周年就是但啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我係咁諗</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n認同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n周年都其他係自己定個日子慶祝姐<br />\n生日就唔同啦，一年得一次，應該佢想幫你慶祝先岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9a0b78dc19a51197b697d1c77aa0ac326f72af9","tid":201784,"uid":36402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T05:09:00.000Z","msg":"要慶祝幾時都得啦<br />\n點解要執著一個日子"},{"pid":"a6cf218e0a75303c906b30cb0052b26afdeb2530","tid":201784,"uid":72891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T05:10:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6dadfbd942b5c6c7eccfcf596a9c3059301a58e2","tid":201784,"uid":68297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T05:11:16.000Z","msg":"如果佢會提早同你慶祝呢"},{"pid":"cb0ad0e1df4518faf947f54321e9014ed6500528","tid":201784,"uid":72796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T05:12:19.000Z","msg":"我個人覺得旅行比特別日子重要，重點應該放係佢交代件事上面"},{"pid":"77c7189326e97cb79cf8681febeab79f1ea1e531","tid":201784,"uid":36813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T05:13:36.000Z","msg":"生日既話就真心過份左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n紀念日就無所謂 返黎補返都ok"},{"pid":"db25ec0709ab6b478e9ba149b9173d48d4f6ddc7","tid":201784,"uid":11515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T05:17:49.000Z","msg":"旅行講真難約好多wor, <br />\n講真，如果知道對方平時係錫自己，<br />\n係咪真係要咁執著果日慶祝？"},{"pid":"4d2ac5690ce690eb13a6f5627b11b03c554ddd9b","tid":201784,"uid":19505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T05:22:21.000Z","msg":"我係咁睇<br />\n<br />\n如果班人係咁難約到<br />\n咁難得有機會可以齊人一起去<br />\n又同你一早講定<br />\n其實就冇乜野<br />\n<br />\n同你慶祝生日就年年都得啦<br />\n成班同學約埋一齊去旅行就唔係年年都有機會啦"},{"pid":"02165355a42983f44a03e0f76604d64124d5f3ce","tid":201784,"uid":4998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T05:24:41.000Z","msg":"連登大戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45e89e324798c59176c0ff35d0316bb213dc8f05","tid":201784,"uid":99114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T05:25:44.000Z","msg":"由佢囉，但調返轉佢都唔認為我會記住其他重要日子"},{"pid":"c05c9a5a2d4b454242b82b84129195e9af7cff41","tid":201784,"uid":73571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T05:26:35.000Z","msg":"既然佢可以就人地日子，點解佢d中同唔可以就佢一日？<br />\n講到尾都係d中同重要過你"},{"pid":"219ff528907a135986c8c31291c67798cacfcaf3","tid":201784,"uid":35698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T05:29:07.000Z","msg":"睇佢點處理啦，始終約一大班人去旅行好難夾日子<br />\n如果佢一早事前講晒出黎，又顯示到自己已經flight過第二啲日子先去都係唔得，佢都唔想嗰日唔喺香港，再加埋出發前認真慶祝返重要日子，咁又無咩問題<br />\n但如果佢一開始就覺得走咗去無問題既話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"543aafa97b376eb2afd83922e5d4f3d26df11e15","tid":201784,"uid":98645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T05:29:25.000Z","msg":"你知道能夠約到好撚多人一齊去旅行係一件幾難嘅事嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 叫佢買啲有心思嘅手信比你啦"},{"pid":"8f0230a1bf5713b19f50041f7b32d4656debdd14","tid":201784,"uid":78432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T05:30:04.000Z","msg":"如果佢一早同你講定<br />\n即係佢本身記得呢個日子<br />\n亦都應該會同你提前慶祝或者補番<br />\n所以根本無野好諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n相反<br />\n無講定 即係根本都唔記得<br />\n咁就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}